Mattis 2023-03-02 1:50 AM
How I became a Hoot Owl: It was back in 2009. My mother lend a rental car because it was winter and the ac of our car did not work. My mother went shopping and I waited for her in the car. She left the radio on so I could listen to music and then Fireflies played. It was such a magical moment, I still remember this moment as a picture. I was maybe 6 years old but I felt that this is something special. I heard the song in the radio a few times but then it disappeared for years because I did not know the song name. Years later, I heard it again in and found the sing name. I listened to it on spotify, opened the artist profile and listened to more songs. After a while I found out about his other projects and he became my favorite artist.
